                    <span>I don't think I fully understood what the true meaning of having a "best friend" was until after reading this book. It gives such insight into what it means to be and to have a Best Friend. It explores the concepts of unconditional love and true acceptance of the people we call our Best Friends. This would be a great book to give to the person in your life that holds the honor of being your Best Friend.</span>
                  
